---
title: Buffalo Chicken Sandwiches with DIY Ranch, Crunchy Slaw and Sweet Potato Fries
description: That spicy chicken sandwich you just can't resist is finally coming at you, hot and ready! It's the real deal – pan-fried chicken tossed in drool-worthy Buffalo sauce on a toasted artisan bun, topped with creamy slaw and oh-so-satisfying ranch. It's time to get messy!
